AI: [Enhanced version]
User: "Too long, make it concise"
AI: [Shorter version, PRIME maintained]
User: "Perfect!"
[Multi-turn refinement in conversation]
3. Validation in Context
Website:
User gets prompt â†’ Uses it â†’ ??? 
[No feedback loop]

Coding Agent:
User gets prompt â†’ Uses it immediately in project
User: "This didn't work for X reason"
AI: [Sees the issue, adjusts prompt]
[Continuous improvement loop]
